          <p>Fleet shows you the current state of every device. Configuration management tools enforce desired state. Together they create a closed loop: Fleet detects drift, your CM tool remediates it, Fleet verifies the fix.</p>
        </div>
        <div purpose="detail-vendors">
          <span class="vendor-tag">Ansible</span>
          <span class="vendor-tag">Puppet</span>
